project_descr: Support Tanah Papua (Papua and West Papua Provinces) to address challenges such as low growth, high poverty rate, low HDI, violence against women, problems on social cohesion, peace building,increasing disparity and to accelerate its development goals.

donor_name: UNITED STATES AGENCY FOR INTERNATIONAL DEVELOPMENT (USAID)
outputs.output_descr: Policy initiatives and capacity building measures piloted in Papua and West Papua in the areas of LED, local governance strengthening, gender-based violence, social cohesion, and government co-sharing
